      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation geometry and operating conditions span the COU envelope; any extrapolation beyond validated range is quantified.",
      "rationale": "Validation was performed on the FDA benchmark pump geometry, which differs from the proprietary VAD impeller in blade count and tip clearance. Geometric similarity is argued qualitatively but not quantified. Achieved level 2."
    },
