      "acceptanceCriteria": "Demonstrated equivalency between simulation input parameters and physical test conditions through documented calibration records and traceability.",
      "rationale": "Inlet boundary conditions were derived from bulk flow measurements without velocity-profile characterization. Equivalency between CFD inlet profile and experimental conditions is assumed, not demonstrated. Epistemic gap at MRL 5."
